                                    eert-<lb/>rijcs.</incipit>
                                <explicit>In <lb/>
                                    <ex>chriſt</ex>o ih<ex>eſ</ex>u onſen here. <lb/> Amen</explicit>
                            </msItem>
                            <msItem n="14.2" class="ban">
                                <title type="supplied">A Good Prayer</title>
                                <rubric>Een goet ghebet.</rubric>
                                <incipit>O here ih<ex>e</ex>ſu <ex>chriſt</ex>e <lb/>die alle tijti
                                    voꝛ <lb/> onſe ſcout gheoffert</incipit>
                                <explicit>des uiants verloſſes <lb/>ende du mi ten ewi-<lb/>ghen leuen
                                    voeres. <lb/> Amen.</explicit>
                                <note>This prayer has not yet been found elsewhere</note>
                            </msItem>
